CDP1802 tools
=============

a18/            assembler, tweaked to compile RCA ASM sources
disasm/         disassembler, tweaked to read binary data
sim18/          simulator, microFORTH nucleus reconstruction, figFORTH,
                UT20 monitor, work in-progress
calc18/         native compiler for a B-like language


NOTE: For the excellent 'Emma 02 Emulator' see 
https://www.emma02.hobby-site.com/index.html, for the original A18 assembler 
see Herb Johnson's site at http://www.retrotechnology.com/memship/a18.html.
Otherwise here is the code. Good luck!
